{"tid":1179604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲駐港總領事冀逃犯條例任何修訂須經正當程序及諮詢","createTime":"2019-05-31T08:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:44:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d1aa56c41d47b0172e03fa6f518030cbf4cce421","tid":1179604,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"澳洲駐港總領事館表示，由於本港修訂《逃犯條例》受到國際社會及公眾強烈關注，期望任何修訂，也要經過正當程序及諮詢，並維繫落實「一國兩制」的信心。<br />\n<br />\n對於特區政府有關《逃犯條例》的最新建議，包括將移交逃門檻提高至刑期7年或以上罪行，以及須由中央機構提出移交，澳洲駐港總領事館發言人回覆本台查詢時表示，不會就個別修訂條文出評論。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，一直密切關注本港修訂《逃犯條例》事宜，澳洲駐港總領事曾向特區政府、行政會議及立法會，提出有關討論。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460315-20190531.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460315-20190531.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=e90f9dd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460315-20190531.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=26ac469a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460315-20190531.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6b1bd6c302d56c56734f249d27760072b9bb874b","tid":1179604,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c854e86bdd567c766a49e9b95b720a4d101a208","tid":1179604,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0944a02bb86f5b620e0bf8fa84dd22292cfa36","tid":1179604,"uid":207208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=456209ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114cf5c811627c520697b7aa2f5c167cfeb96cff","tid":1179604,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499404994fe198fa3f10c0069cebf08f7181d2b8","tid":1179604,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"澳洲出手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c1fb3c095fd8b6bd706f5c7a12a05d44620a72","tid":1179604,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"咁既立法會同咁既政府, 點會仲有正當程序"},{"pid":"e3d213671312776e8266af304722d97891f1348c","tid":1179604,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭：我年年考第一好打得 你地個個唔識野"}]}